query:
SELECT id, componentCode, componentName, componentLocation, conditionRating, createdAt, updatedAt 
FROM assessments 
WHERE componentName IS NOT NULL AND componentName != '' 
ORDER BY updatedAt DESC 
LIMIT 10;
